Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想感受風…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想感受比這世界上能感受到的 都要凜冽的風…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:23.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所有的歡笑 所有的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:23.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}笑顔も涙もきっと全て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:30.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一切都是為了與你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:30.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君に出会うためだった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:49.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}漱漱而下的淚水 在風中飄散
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:49.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}こぼれ行く涙風が連れて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.97,0:00:57.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}以生疏的動作 無數次伸出手去追求
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.97,0:00:57.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}慣れない仕草でその先へ何度も手を伸ばした
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:02.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}那個不善於表達而受傷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:02.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}言葉足らずで傷つけた人よ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.01,0:01:08.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}現在已經背負起不可磨滅的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.01,0:01:08.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}もう取り消せない過去を背負って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:12.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}踏出了新的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:12.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}踏み出して行くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:18.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}笑顔も涙もきっと全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:18.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所有的歡笑 所有的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:25.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君に出会うための理由だった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:25.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一切都是為了與你相遇的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.26,0:01:31.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}明日があるたったそれだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.26,0:01:31.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只因為這一個理由 就是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:37.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}僕ら生きる意味になって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:37.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}那將成為我們生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:44.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}そしてまた日が照らすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能將時間段限定到哪個範圍？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮兹好像只知道會在今晚發生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 肯定會出現在這個區域的某個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請謹慎行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟之前發生過綁架燈里的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼大事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這已經是個大事了好不…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平沒必要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那時候我應該和你一起行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 在這關鍵時刻我不能在現場真是抱歉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相支援才是一個團隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有我一個人沒有為團隊出力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為戰鬥單位來說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先正確的掌握自身的戰力才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:03:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在留在種子島上做你和你的Livlaster的能力檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是你的最重要的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果進行得順利的話 仲夏騎士團的戰力將會變成2倍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你了哦 哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳言說的沒錯呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的傳言？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個女人能夠追風逐電一樣地操縱機車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得沒人能勝過你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實就是如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:03:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪所學校的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有上學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有輛不錯的機車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是有錢人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這風很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:23.18,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\c&HFEFEFE&\pos(226,444)}風之{\c&HE8E1A3&}星{\r\c&HFFFFFF&}上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 毬村老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為這個項目提供研究資金的「Robin」是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 幾年前我曾研究利用經顱磁刺激治療法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來研究如何控制睡眠研究對象的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是讓人來做自己喜歡的夢的系統嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果完成的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以在精神醫學和臨床心理學上實現各種各樣的應用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這個研究感興趣提出援助的人就是Robin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是Robin這個名字是個人名還是法人名這點我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個項目名之所以叫「Install」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指將夢植入的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.91,0:05:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡啊 真央
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你的光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你 對毬村老師的稱呼以及那態度…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的啦 她是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚是為何而來？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又缺零用錢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰明人就不多說廢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要更快的機車…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來 皮兹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下…掛飾卡上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好純情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起哲平呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他會那麼在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後可要小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 哲平對於不在現場而自責這事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我個人而言 倒是有點高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經完全進入催眠狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師為什麼會執著於這孩子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留住這孩子對於這個項目來說是非常重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在正處於你的內心深處…一個自由的靈魂的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是如何看待你的日常生活的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡機車的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想開得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.31,0:07:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機車給予了你自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是對於現在的生活你沒有感到不安嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為真正的自我身在別處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的自我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的自我是指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡非工作人員是禁止入內的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去聯絡警衛員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看這腦核磁共振譜的變化…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能相信這是同一人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毬村老師…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也是Designer's Child吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們行星齒輪裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是揭示世界之夢之人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夏大地嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在這裡解決掉他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是讓ALBION失常的地球人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想陪他玩玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他是Neoteny
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要忘記這點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看牠們游得多歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看牠們游得多歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠們一定不知道牠們會死 所以才會游得那麼歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不知道會更加幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是生命終歸一死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一樣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡意味著作為一個生命體是不完全的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為什麼會認為不會死的人才是真正的人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為事實就是如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們並非是真正的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以肯定會死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你 對於肯定會死這事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是怎樣想的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不對自己是那種生命短暫的生物而感到可悲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人曾對我說過「死的時候一定要含笑而終」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你們這種生命體也只能含笑而終了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是你這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要強詞奪理了 Neoteny
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我以前是田徑部的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是種子島的Livlaster嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢舉起雙手 把槍給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負就留在下次了 地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架機器很快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你乘過的任何機車都要快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道如何操作吧 LIEBAN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和那位Neoteny做一了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Abreaction！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MM車檢測到反應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Machine Goodfellow啟動地點 中心點特定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Machine Goodfellow在水裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小華曾說過他們會出現在這個區域
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他們就一定會在這附近出現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個人一定會來和我決一勝負的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們接觸過了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:12:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine Ordinary 射出！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她果然來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來決一勝負吧 地球人！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打水戰嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳進海裡是你失策了 原田徑部隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就結束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放跑她了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是真正的自我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這就是我真正的速度！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認到AEO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是KILL-T-GANG Type-4！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現地點位於第一防禦圈的o區域內
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區域內的衝擊兵器開始迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓他跑了嗎 大地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終止哲平的測試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我就這樣去迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什麼 哲平？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天海道中應該已經裝備了和這架機器合體的衝擊兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(870,660)}Expand
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是開發用的原型機的改造機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說為什麼你會知道有那東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 你所乘坐的荒武者自換裝成那架機體後還沒試飛過啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它已經不叫荒武者了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫Nebula Engine Ordinary！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經做好了基本武器的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還沒有得到准許
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學部長！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的哲平做得到的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去吧 司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長放跑的敵人必須由我來解決才行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相支援才是一個團隊啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地 你能聽到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我下命令 隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解 隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜祭知事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送Nebula上去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真假啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Expansion Sequence啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nebula Engine從彩虹號上分離
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(740,660)}Regenbogen
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認到Nebula Engine的能量填充
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這光芒…是生命力能量？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是LIEBAN嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Livlaster嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了！Neoteny！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的速度是追不上我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這速度…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用眼是追不上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去感受…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命力能量的流動…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一位Neoteny！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nebula Engine成功擊退了KILL-T-GANG Type-4
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定會成為最棒的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要讓他搶回去了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有另外一個Neoteny
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是Livlaster所發生的能量到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像一股舒服的微風…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒 毬村老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:21:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:21:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們到底是什麼人啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我們去聯繫警察吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.11,0:22:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事就算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你回來 真央姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.78,0:22:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在等我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.59,0:22:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.27,0:22:48.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ふわり風は彼方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.27,0:22:48.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}清風徐徐吹向遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.57,0:22:54.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}涙も連れて行ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.57,0:22:54.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}請把我的眼淚也一起帶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:23:01.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}星ほどの思い出たちだって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:23:01.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使是那些堪比繁星的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:05.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}いいことばっかじゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:05.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}也不全是快樂的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:13.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}瞬いて　君と出逢えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:13.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}那個閃爍的瞬間 我與你相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:20.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ねぇ　こんなに近くで遠い今日が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:20.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}今天 這個近在咫尺又如此遙遠的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:31.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}始まる合図はぽつりわたしを呼ぶ声聞こえてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:31.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我聽到了那個開始的信號 在輕輕地呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:40.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}愛してるよりもっと形のない言葉探して行くね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:40.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}要尋找比「我愛你」更加飄渺的情話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:43.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}すぐ側に歩き出して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:43.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我從你身邊走出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:50.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}さよならよりもそっと涙が紡いだ恋は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:50.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}比「再見」更會在不經意間催人淚下的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:54.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}明日も右ポケットに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:54.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}明天依然緊攥在右邊口袋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:23:57.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}世界は声に溢れて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:23:57.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}世界充滿著美妙的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:03.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}やっと見つけたんだ　君のとなりを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:03.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我終於找到了與你並肩的位置
